{
  "stem": "23096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All I remember is the two-- I'm-- I-- positive there was two, two dead Germans laying there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when we went in, and this-- the first thing, more or less, we saw was this-- like, a courtyard and all these dead bodies laying in kind of, more or less, a group.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went back out to our wire truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I got my camera.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a little Baby Brownie, plastic Baby Brownie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It took 128 film, which is probably about the size of a 35 millimeter today.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had one picture left on the roll.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's all the film I had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was the first thing I saw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that was-- I took that picture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that picture, even though it was the first thing I saw, was quite a famous picture because that is the exact same picture that was shown all over the world of Eisenhower and Patton and all his entourage viewing the bodies, these bodies laying there.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Except my picture didn't have any of the, the generals standing around looking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I always tell the people when I talk to them when I give a lecture on it, my picture is showing what they saw.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the other picture shows who saw it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But then we start walking, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There weren't very many [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] prisoners alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "These were all-- had been shot just hours before the, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- [CRYING] they had taken all the prisoners who could walk and marched them out and-- because they knew-- they knew we were coming.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And these people were-- probably were the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] weren't strong enough or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they just shot them there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
